/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Some of the weapons that need to be designed include:<br>
<br>
twin katanas -   Nagasuri the demonic samurai's weapon of choice. He uses these katanas using the Nitouichi style  (2 sword technique) and his special move with his weapons is called Jigen Ryu  (Lightning Strike technique)<br>
<br>
Wakizashi - AKA &quot;Kodachi (Aoshi from Rurouni Kenshin's weapons of choice) a much smaller version of a katana, not usually used as a weapon of choice, mostly used to commit seppuko or &quot;ritual suicide&quot;, when samurai fail to defeat their opponent. they use this to kill themselves so their pride and honor remains safe.This weapon is for Nagasuri, but he only uses it once, he commits suicide  towards the end of the anime series when he fails to defeat the main hero, Ganon.<br>
<br>
Japanese Prayer wheel - A chinese or japanese polearm, looks a lot like a quarterstaff but has about 3 - 5 solid metal cricles on the top of one end that have magic enscribed spells written on  them. This weapon is for Sunaj, a demon that wears a  cloak and a sinister looking ceramic mask to his his ugly face. His special attack is summoned once he chants the words on the staff, its basically a blast of acid,called  Acid bath.<br>
<br>
zweihander  sword - (a really big sword with no guard, an example would be  knightmare's soul edge sword in soul calibur II) - this weapon is for Tolpa the  demonic japanese beserker his zweihander has a long handle and a  gigantic blad, it's name  will be called the Mammoth Sword. When Tolpa waves his sword in a circle formation in the air, it creates a  huge ball of fire called Blazing Fury, his special attack.<br>
<br>
Flail - (2 - spiked mace iron balls attached to a chain and a handle) - This weapon is for Meduro, the 4th demonic warlord who uses this weapon for a special attack called &quot; World Smasher&quot;, which sends a tremendous  geometric shockwave through the ground towards the target.<br>
<br>
Kusari - gamma (AKA ) scythe with chain or kunai with chain - a small sickle/sycthe attached to a long chain  at one end and  a small weight on  other end of the chain - This is the main weapon  for a ninja. He  uses other weapons  as well such as the ninja-to, shurikens and a ninja weapon called a  shikomi - zu  for the ninja assassin named Ermac.<br>
<br>
- I still need to think of a special attack for him, using this weapon. (Anubis from Ronin Warrirors had this weapon, his attack was called &quot;Quake with Fear&quot; or something similar to that. Any ideas for a special attack using this weapon are greatly welcomed.<br>
<br>
Boomerang - this weapon is  for Jutaro the man with incredible super human strength. It is made of solid metal. It looks just like a regular boomerang except it is very large and has a metalic color to it.  (Sango's boomerang from Inuyasha, its about that size if u want to compare). Jutaro's special attack I still need to think of one.<br>
<br>
Royal Battle Axe - this is for the Lord Verok (aka) Lord Adrastos Verok, a former human king, now turned demon black knight.  the only thing for this axe i was thinking of is that it needs to be double sides or a twin axe and its blade and handle is large. He Uses this weapon for his special attack called Soul Driver.<br>
<br>
